netdroid is a fast multi-threaded network utility. It performs network scan, detecting every host ip and mac address. Port scanning, detecting well-known ports and the service running on ports. In addition, several network utilities are provided within the app for testing connectivity like: ping, and netstat for display of smartphone connections. Finally, netdroid displays all ip, network, and wifi configuration on local network.

==Features==
1- IP Scanner 
2- Port Scanner
3- Ip Configuration (localhost)
4- Wifi Configuration
5- Ping Utility
6- Netstat Utility (local connections)
7- IP Configuration (loca / public)
8- Location Detection
9- ISP detection

